{"tid":228440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台料未來一兩小時有驟雨及狂風雷暴","createTime":"2017-05-04T01:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T02:45:02.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40d191cddf42bf3e7d51b5d7be6d337117039827","tid":228440,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1328479_1_L_20170504085548.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1328479_1_L_20170504085548.jpg&h=9c65dddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天文台在上午8時50分發出雷暴警告，有效時間至上午10時45分，預料香港有幾陣狂風雷暴。<br />\n<br />\n天文台表示，一道雷雨帶正橫過珠江口一帶，預料未來一兩小時本港會有驟雨及狂風雷暴，部分地區雨勢頗大。市民請提高警惕。預料高達每小時70公里或以上的陣風吹襲香港。"},{"pid":"81f1edf043ec6c4eef06c0842f39a2d7e63b337b","tid":228440,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:25:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"849829e15a67100719b1a7dd7953fc96d95b39aa","tid":228440,"uid":68236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:29:24.000Z","msg":"個天陰得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25430255e123014e785209dcadce2ccadc79aea1","tid":228440,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:30:01.000Z","msg":"新界落緊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0262e8dc4be53334cc19488bc3f1a07d816ba65d","tid":228440,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:31:12.000Z","msg":"幾時有風打 ?"},{"pid":"42fbbdb1b716e410654f5858784dfad19d572ca1","tid":228440,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:32:04.000Z","msg":"岩岩沙田落緊"},{"pid":"bc4239fe0f9b0aec260e93823300e3c55342aaa8","tid":228440,"uid":7421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:33:15.000Z","msg":"陰到咁 一出街就立痴痴 想留係屋企嘆冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />